title: NEFF Presents: SuckerFace Challenge
description: **SuckerFace Challenge** Every Monday until 2012 NEFF will be launching a new contest on Facebook brought to you by Mr. Neff. Take a video of you and your friends competing in a SuckerFace Challenge. We are looking for the most creative way to cram packs of Kool-Aid in your mouth and make a SuckerFace. Submit the videos to info@neffheadwear.com.
